Can my username be saved as a cookie?








Help yourself


A username can be saved as a cookie. Please note that if you save both your username and password, and you access sensitive public records content, you will be asked to enter your password again. This re-authentication process will only be required once per session.
A forgotten username can be emailed with validation of email address. A forgotten password can be changed with validation of email address.


