We are dedicated to bringing you insights around today's key global business topics – from increasing risk and regulatory complexity to transformative technology and business models.


	        Answers On Thomsonreuters.com














What makes Thomson Reuters the Answer Company? (1:23)












Partnership and collaboration



Integrating into an innovation ecosystem


	How the Thomson Reuters Lab™ in Waterloo, Canada partners with startups, universities, and clients to create cutting edge business solutions.




Joining forces with leading law firms


	We partnered with Clifford Chance to create a solution for smarter, faster OTC contracts for global banks.







Creating a blockchain ecosystem


	How we collaborate with customers and innovators to explore proofs-of-concept and the benefits of distributed ledger technology.







Breaking news with machine learning


	Our teams worked together to build and train a social media monitoring tool that collects and verifies breaking news on Twitter.







Enabling agile KYC in Africa


	We developed a client onboarding tool with partners in South Africa that can be extended to other African jurisdictions.













