So, we're quite encouraged by them. And they are less, frankly, head count dependent in all cases. And they're right in the heart of the world that's changing so fast right now. When you think about the geopolitical uncertainty and you think about the regulatory changes that are afoot, we think that bodes quite well for these businesses because when things change, that's the time our customers turn to companies like us for the trusted answers that they need to navigate those changes. So, we're encouraged that those trends can indeed continue.
