Indirect Tax
Keep up with constantly changing sales and use tax, VAT, GST, as well as country and industry-specific indirect taxes around the globe. With the broadest and deepest coverage of tax content in over 14,500 tax jurisdictions in over 180 countries, we consolidate your work with a solution that offers proven results. Thomson Reuters ONESOURCE manages tax compliance easily, cost-effectively and efficiently.
View Product Details >

International Tax Research
Gain a deep understanding of the requirements of doing business in every region of the world with the most comprehensive information solutions to serve your expanding needs. Get up to speed on tax treaties, transfer pricing, tax laws, and global tax strategies. Access OECD models and IBFD content as well as our own WorldTrade Executive and WG&L analysis and treatises.
View Product Details >

International Trade
For members of the international trade community, research materials, support and tools from our Boskage, WorldTrade Executive and WG&L experts are now available together on Thomson Reuters Checkpoint®, the leading online information service for tax, accounting and finance professionals. We understand that yours is a complex and ever-changing industry, and as a result our products are updated as laws, policies, government texts or supplements change.
View Product Details >

Live Seminars & Conferences
Seminars and week-long conferences from leading providers of tax and accounting education, presented by Checkpoint Learning from Thomson Reuters. Nationally recognized speakers and hands-on practitioners provide the latest in continuing education and networking.
View Product Details >

Marketing Solutions
Acquire and retain clients, position your firm as a thought leader, and grow a more profitable practice. Marketing solutions include digital and print newsletters, tax and estate planning guides, custom articles, content for your website, social media marketing tools and other business development tools and services from our leading brands – Checkpoint Marketing for Firms and Web Builder CS.

Mastersaf
This comprehensive tax and accounting solution helps Brazilian corporations keep up with corporate accounting needs.
View Product Details >

myPay Solutions
Payroll processing for your accounting firm’s clients. Accurate client reporting, revenue sharing and journal entries integrate with your write-up or trial balance software. Increase your business and boost client retention without having to physically process payrolls.
